  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To establish a serial ascertainement of specimens from patients with bone sarcomas to be used
      in ongoing cytogenetic and molecular genetic analyses. These data will be integrated and
      correlated with the established Orthopaedic Service clinical database.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
